Meet TRACTIAN: the online maintenance system that combines smart sensors for condition monitoring with maintenance management software.

Through the app, you can follow the routine of your industrial equipment and get alerts and diagnostics that make your maintenance more worry-free and assertive.

No matter the size of your industry, it deserves the most cutting-edge tools in maintenance management and online monitoring.

Only with TRACTIAN App you can:

Create a Work Order in less than 1 minute - faster than texting;
Receive automatic alerts at the slightest sign of an anomaly or potential failure in your machine;
Customize procedures according to your needs, with immediate access to checklists and inspection activities;
Send photos, documents, links and other resources to the whole maintenance team or specific employees whenever you want;
Visualize all vibration, temperature, energy consumption and hour meter data of your assets.

descriptionHtml:
Meet TRACTIAN: the online maintenance system that combines smart sensors for condition monitoring with maintenance management software.

Through the app, you can follow the routine of your industrial equipment and get alerts and diagnostics that make your maintenance more worry-free and assertive.

No matter the size of your industry, it deserves the most cutting-edge tools in maintenance management and online monitoring.

Only with TRACTIAN App you can:

Create a Work Order in less than 1 minute - faster than texting;
Receive automatic alerts at the slightest sign of an anomaly or potential failure in your machine;
Customize procedures according to your needs, with immediate access to checklists and inspection activities;
Send photos, documents, links and other resources to the whole maintenance team or specific employees whenever you want;
Visualize all vibration, temperature, energy consumption and hour meter data of your assets.

Here's how it works: We map your critical assets and connect them to sensors that can accurately measure indicators such as temperature, vibration, hour meters, and energy consumption.

You don't even have to go to the machine to collect the data - the information is sent in real time directly to the app. You can monitor everything remotely, avoiding risks for your maintenance team.

Plus, all data is automatically backed up in the cloud via our 2g/3g network, with no need for IT approval, industrial Wi-Fi or specific infrastructure.

Your spreadsheets will be embarrassed: with our powerful and intuitive CMMS, you can leave the chaos behind and centralize your maintenance so you can focus on the stuff that really matters.

While TRACTIAN's online monitoring sensors and artificial intelligence do all the hard work and increase the availability of your machines, you can take that coffee break and enjoy your stress-free work routine.

Our solution covers more than 100 machine categories, including:

ELECTRIC MOTORS: unbalance, misalignment and resonance faults are quickly identified;
MOTOR PUMPS: receive alerts for over-temperature and unbalance symptoms;
COMPRESSORS: whether volumetric, piston or screw, all will be monitored;
FANS: from belt misalignment to bearing defects, TRACTIAN's sensors do not miss a thing;
BEARINGS: high temperature? Worn out? Our system tells you when these and other common bearing failures will happen.

Ready to be even more in control of your machines?

Leave in the past the downtime and headaches caused by unreliable equipment. TRACTIAN has the solution for the present and the future of your industry.

Download the app now and check out the prices and plans of the fastest growing industrial startup in Latin America.
descriptionShort: Asset Management and Online Monitoring all in one, at your fingertips.
